{"tid":1233621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母呀陳浩天  你條仆街又想走出嚟騎劫議程","createTime":"2019-06-16T19:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T05:50:37.000Z","uid":2748,"like":25,"dislike":120,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab4656d9345ac0d61711256e6a537a25efa2278","tid":1233621,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:57:13.000Z","msg":"明係抄陳雲講嘅嘢又要扮撚曬先知咁, 大家一定要提防呢一條友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2GDxsp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2GDxsp.png&h=3245fb77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cd5AzFK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcd5AzFK.png&h=b58d90a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：據說烏龜陳聽到我的大阪示威之後，想去連登加入。各位小心這個恐怖主義社團人，遠離。<br />\n至於偽港獨是誰支援的，大家心知肚明。<br />\n他一定會用港獨牌來掩蓋請求特朗普幫手的熱心說話，一群熱心的人會被共產黨引導之後，被外國傳媒稱為港獨支持者，與藏獨疆獨搞在一起。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陳雲：小心這些共匪毒害議程。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">  <strong>大家一定要小心 唔好畀一啲面目模糊嘅偽港獨派騎劫, 尤其係陳浩天,無妄齋</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f021a2f5f954f0bb0894388ba214dc78ec0d99f6","tid":1233621,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3300254bcc19a8e989be6ed408f3efa2bb81abc7","tid":1233621,"uid":15625,"like":27,"dislike":41,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:09:25.000Z","msg":"陳云根依d傻佬都有人吹捧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你依d就真係鬼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c880ab47935e20667937e1d626093611c8e7adaa","tid":1233621,"uid":650,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca39f8ec84713b7f34ae7a68e458556f62cbd7b","tid":1233621,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1e9581e979a6b6bc08757b65a1186bcf215d70","tid":1233621,"uid":2748,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:14:09.000Z","msg":"陳雲：今日早上我寫過，香港人要去G20 高峰會抗議，請求特朗普幫助香港獲得民主普選。不久之後，美國國務卿龐佩奧表明，特朗普會在高峰會與習近平談及香港示威的問題。香港正式提上中美衝突的議程！<br />\n我的建議，竟然這麼快得到美國的反應。各位遊覽大阪的朋友，請溫和地請求特朗普總統幫助香港。例如舉牌說：President Trump, please liberate Hong Kong. <br />\n特朗普是英雄人物，一定會幫手的。"},{"pid":"76497add5b1f1192b96347d89071973cac6564f7","tid":1233621,"uid":2748,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:16:45.000Z","msg":"陳浩天，你條港獨友話同人私底下傾左兩個月，你老母早唔講遲唔講，係等到陳云根出左四個post先嚟講？<br />\n唔好扮撚曬野啦"},{"pid":"f45e0bf77d2521cc7367cd5e1f6304799a8d8057","tid":1233621,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995a2b5e9ece1866ad02459be4ef821d71f3e6dc","tid":1233621,"uid":15984,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:24:08.000Z","msg":"連登當年話香港國成立之後，陳浩天最啱做第一任總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee268caa2ff10b374907cade781ad71daf68ed77","tid":1233621,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7345ebde8a691bdb08cc50fe7fa7f95d164da67b","tid":1233621,"uid":15625,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:29:29.000Z","msg"