,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ab4656d9345ac0d61711256e6a537a25efa2278","tid":1233621,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:57:13.000Z","msg":"明係抄陳雲講嘅嘢又要扮撚曬先知咁, 大家一定要提防呢一條友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V2GDxsp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV2GDxsp.png&h=3245fb77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cd5AzFK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcd5AzFK.png&h=b58d90a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：據說烏龜陳聽到我的大阪示威之後，想去連登加入。各位小心這個恐怖主義社團人，遠離。<br />\n至於偽港獨是誰支援的，大家心知肚明。<br />\n他一定會用港獨牌來掩蓋請求特朗普幫手的熱心說話，一群熱心的人會被共產黨引導之後，被外國傳媒稱為港獨支持者，與藏獨疆獨搞在一起。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陳雲：小心這些共匪毒害議程。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">  <strong>大家一定要小心 唔好畀一啲面目模糊嘅偽港獨派騎劫, 尤其係陳浩天,無妄齋</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:32:51.000Z","msg":"陳浩天同鄺俊宇一樣，一日到黑想做巴基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019deb6ae15219a61c2c4cb2d22fc99fe31cc51a","tid":1233621,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ef7eb77dcef34234d038f13d9c350ff282e75e","tid":1233621,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T14:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/de